name: Listened to MOSES: Secret battles of the Mega Man gods

content.html:
Exodus 1-11! The Bible’s Luke/Obi-Wan duo! Made it to Book 2! REALLY important book! Moses rises, falls, rises into one of the world’s biggest heroes Plagues are more metal than you’ve ever realized!
